T1  - STRUCTURAL CHANGE AND AGGREGATE EMPLOYMENT FLUCTUATIONS IN CHINA
AU  - Yao, Wen
AU  - Zhu, Xiaodong
Y1  - 2021/02/01
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12486
T2  - International Economic Review
