T1  - GLOBAL GAMES WITH STRATEGIC SUBSTITUTES
AU  - Harrison, Rodrigo
AU  - Jara-Moroni, Pedro
Y1  - 2021/02/01
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12481
T2  - International Economic Review
