T1  - ENTREPRENEURSHIP AND INCOME DISTRIBUTION DYNAMICS: WHY IS THE INCOME SHARE OF TOP INCOME EARNERS ACYCLICAL OVER THE BUSINESS CYCLE?
AU  - Kwark, Noh-Sun
AU  - Ma, Eunseong
Y1  - 2021/02/01
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12489
